This is a common problem in the field of neural networks, and as such, the paper could fit into several sub-categories. However, given that the paper focuses on the use of extended backpropagation algorithm, which is a common technique in the field of neural networks, it is most likely to be classified under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper deals with the use of cost functions and optimization techniques, which are also common topics in the field of machine learning, and as such, it could also be classified under cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with the approximation of analytical functions and solving differential equations, which are common applications of neural networks, and as such, it could be classified under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper deals with the use of regular grids and spacing, which are common topics in the field of signal processing, and as such, it could also be classified under cs.SI (Signal and Image Processing).
